meta.name: Arginine-Dipeptide
meta.description:
This dataset contains multiple conformations of a single Arginine amino acid,
terminated with two peptide bonds.

The map is built using the [Sketch-Map](https://doi.org/10.1073/pnas.1108486108)
dimensionality reduction algorithm  on
[SOAP](https://doi.org/10.1103/PhysRevB.87.184115) descriptors.
references: Berlin ab initio amino acid database, http://aminoaciddb.rz-berlin.mpg.de/
*"First-principles data set of 45,892 isolated and cation-coordinated conformers of 20 proteinogenic amino acids"*. Sci Data 3, 160009 (2016). https://doi.org/10.1038/sdata.2016.9
*"Mapping and classifying molecules from a high-throughput structural database"*. J Cheminform 9, 6 (2017). https://doi.org/10.1186/s13321-017-0192-4
